            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 1 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive. The script targets the weight of the day that follows you into bed — the replaying thoughts, the worries that crowd close in the dark, the mind that won't switch off. Use it lying down, at bedtime, before the lights go out."
